<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.204534>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 6. 1, Stenolis polygramma (Bates, 1872); 2, Stenolis gilvolineata sp. nov.; 3, Stenolis angulata (Fabricius, 1801); 4, Stenolis flavoguttata sp. nov.; 5, Stenolis inclusa (Bates, 1885); 6, Stenolis xanthostigma sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/204534/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.204535>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7 – 12. 7, Stenolis calligramma (Bates, 1872); 8, Stenolis tavakiliani sp. nov.; 9, Stenolis pulverea (Bates, 1881); 10, Stenolis theobromae (Lara and Shenefelt, 1964); 11, Stenolis vigintiguttata (Bates, 1885) new comb.; 12, Stenolis multimacula sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/204535/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.204536>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 – 17. 13, Stenolis giesberti sp. nov.; 14, Stenolis marcelae sp. nov.; 15, Stenolis nearnsi sp. nov.; 16, Stenolis laetifica (Bates, 1872); 17, Stenolis polytaenia (Bates, 1885)." ;
